Selenium Automation Project – SauceDemo Testing
I built an automation test script using Python + Selenium WebDriver to validate core functionalities of the SauceDemo application (https://www.saucedemo.com).
Features Automated:
✅ Login Validation – Verified successful login with valid credentials
✅ Add to Cart – Added product and validated cart badge update
✅ Checkout Flow – Completed purchase and verified confirmation message
✅ Logout Functionality – Ensured user is redirected back to login page
Tech Stack:
•	Python
•	Selenium WebDriver
•	WebDriverWait (Explicit Waits)
•	ChromeDriver (via webdriver-manager)
